title: Frozen Library of the Undead Knight
story: For many years the library of the Undead Knight remained abandoned. Recently a party of bandits rediscovered it, making it their center of operation.

notes.text: A battered wooden door with a keyhole on the southern wall of the small chamber.
A ticking clockwork machine, turns out to be a mimic when the lever is pulled.
A magic niddle hovering in the middle of the small chamber.
A battered crate with a golden medallion.
A carving on the wall, totally destroyed by bandit vandals.
